OL,3,CStarmer 'like rabbit in headlights',
OL,4,Csays Swinney as SNP demand fuel price
OL,5,Ccuts
OL,7,FThe First Minister has said Sir Keir
OL,8,FStarmer is "like a rabbit in the
OL,9,Fheadlights" as the SNP launch a
OL,10,Fcampaign to demand the UK Government
OL,11,Fcut fuel prices
OL,13,FFirst Minister and SNP leader John
OL,14,FSwinney will launch an SNP campaign on
OL,15,FTuesday to call for the UK Government
OL,16,Fto reduce fuel prices amid the energy
OL,17,Fcrisis.
OL,26,@pD@LOUqD@KO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
