OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1775523444
OL,3,CStarmer 'like rabbit in headlights',
OL,4,Csays Swinney as SNP demand fuel price
OL,5,Ccuts
OL,7,FMr Swinney said: "Scotland is an
OL,8,Fenergy superpower but as part of the
OL,9,FUK we are facing soaring costs every
OL,10,Ftime we fill up our cars. Whether
OL,11,FLabour like it or not, their failures
OL,12,Fon energy will be the defining issue
OL,13,Fof this election campaign.
OL,15,F"While other governments across Europe
OL,16,Fhave taken swift and decisive action,
OL,17,FKeir Starmer has done nothing ` he is
OL,18,Flike a rabbit in the headlights and it
OL,19,Fis the people of Scotland who are
OL,20,Fpaying the price."
OL,26,@oD@ROUwD@AOU|D@RO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
