CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1775523444
OL,3,CStarmer 'like rabbit in headlights',
OL,4,Csays Swinney as SNP demand fuel price
OL,5,Ccuts
OL,7,FIn a speech in Leith, the First
OL,8,FMinister will call on Sir Keir to
OL,9,Ffollow SNP suggested actions including
OL,10,Fimmediately scrapping the planned fuel
OL,11,Fduty increase and removing VAT from
OL,12,Ffuel duty for the duration of the
OL,13,Fcrisis.
OL,15,FThe UK has been facing rising fuel
OL,16,Fprices due to the US-Israeli conflict
OL,17,Fwith Iran.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
