PN,30604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1775523444
OL,3,CStarmer 'like rabbit in headlights',
OL,4,Csays Swinney as SNP demand fuel price
OL,5,Ccuts
OL,7,FMr Swinney continued: "Every time
OL,8,Fpeople in Scotland go to the petrol
OL,9,Fpumps, they are seeing first-hand the
OL,10,Fconsequences of a deeply incompetent
OL,11,FLabour Prime Minister who is asleep at
OL,12,Fthe wheel and refusing to act.
OL,14,F"Labour simply cannot be trusted with
OL,15,FScotland's energy wealth. Westminster
OL,16,Fcontrol means we pay some of the
OL,17,Fhighest energy bills in Europe, face
OL,18,Fsoaring petrol prices while jobs in
OL,19,Four energy sector are lost.
OL,26,@oD@WOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1775523444
OL,3,CStarmer 'like rabbit in headlights',
OL,4,Csays Swinney as SNP demand fuel price
OL,5,Ccuts
OL,7,F"With the fresh start of independence,
OL,8,FScotland's vast energy wealth will
OL,9,Fwork for the people of Scotland and be
OL,10,Fused to bring down bills ` that is
OL,11,Fwhat the SNP is offering at this
OL,12,Felection.
OL,14,F"And our message to the UK Labour
OL,15,FGovernment in the face of the energy
OL,16,Fcrisis is clear ` cut fuel prices now."
OL,18,FA Government spokesperson said:
OL,19,F"Families and businesses will be
OL,20,Fworried about the impact of conflict
OL,21,Fin the Middle East here at home.
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOUxD@gO]{D@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
