OL,3,CStarmer 'like rabbit in headlights',
OL,4,Csays Swinney as SNP demand fuel price
OL,5,Ccuts
OL,7,F"The Government is determined to fight
OL,8,Fpeople's corner.
OL,10,F"To support drivers at the budget we
OL,11,Fextended the 5p fuel duty cut from
OL,12,Fthis month to September."
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@AOUtD@YO]
